title: Woman infected with eye worm known only in cattle
text:
Woman infected with eye worm known only in cattle  24 
An Oregon woman has become the first person worldwide known to have had an eye infestation by a tiny worm species previously seen only in cattle, an indication that humans may be more vulnerable than previously thought to such infections. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
